  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is a nice hack that shows we are not that far from being able to do server side rendering.\r\n\r\nAs already discussed the only drawback is that it relies on client.search() (raw search results) and this would be too complex for users to determine what to do in here.\r\n\r\nAsynchronous server side rendering seems to be a common issue, see https://www.google.com/search?q=react+asynchronous+server+side+render maybe there are non-explored gems here.",
